---
// HowItWorksSteps — three-step explainer block matching the v0.3 mockup
// Section 2. Owner Builder–specific copy: enrol → learn → assess.
//
// Could be parameterised per productLine in future; for now hardcoded
// since every Owner Builder course follows the same flow.
//
// Zero JS shipped. Card hover-lift comes from global.css.
---

<section id="section-2" class="py-14 lg:py-20 bg-base-200/50 border-t border-base-300">
  <div class="mx-auto max-w-5xl px-4">
    <h2 class="font-display text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold mb-8">How does the course work?</h2>

    <div class="alert bg-primary/5 border border-primary/20 mb-10 text-base-content">
      <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="stroke-primary shrink-0 h-6 w-6" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" aria-hidden="true">
        <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M13 16h-1v-4h-1m1-4h.01M21 12a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z" />
      </svg>
      <p>
        Enrol online through ABE Education, complete five units of competency at
        your own pace, then sit the assessment. Your RTO partner verifies your
        work and issues your Statement of Attainment. You then take that
        certificate to the regulator with your White Card and supporting
        documents to apply for your Owner Builder Permit.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-5">

      <div class="card bg-base-100 border border-base-300 shadow-sm">
        <div class="card-body p-6">
          <div class="flex items-center gap-3 mb-3">
            <span class="font-display text-3xl font-bold text-primary">01</span>
            <span class="badge badge-outline badge-sm">Enrol</span>
          </div>
          <h3 class="card-title font-display text-lg">Enrol online</h3>
          <p class="text-sm text-base-content/80">
            Sign up through ABE Education, set your password, and you'll get
            straight access to the course. You'll need a Unique Student
            Identifier (USI) to enrol — required for all nationally recognised
            training. Free to create at
            <a href="https://www.usi.gov.au" class="link link-primary">usi.gov.au</a>.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="card bg-base-100 border border-base-300 shadow-sm">
        <div class="card-body p-6">
          <div class="flex items-center gap-3 mb-3">
            <span class="font-display text-3xl font-bold text-primary">02</span>
            <span class="badge badge-outline badge-sm">Learn</span>
          </div>
          <h3 class="card-title font-display text-lg">Work through five units</h3>
          <p class="text-sm text-base-content/80">
            The course is fully online and self-paced. Read the learner
            materials, watch the supporting videos, and complete each unit in
            order. Pause and pick up where you left off — your progress is
            saved.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="card bg-base-100 border border-base-300 shadow-sm">
        <div class="card-body p-6">
          <div class="flex items-center gap-3 mb-3">
            <span class="font-display text-3xl font-bold text-primary">03</span>
            <span class="badge badge-outline badge-sm">Assess</span>
          </div>
          <h3 class="card-title font-display text-lg">Sit the assessment</h3>
          <p class="text-sm text-base-content/80">
            Each unit has a written assessment you complete inside the platform.
            Once you've passed all five, your RTO reviews your work and issues
            your Statement of Attainment — emailed to you and recorded against
            your USI.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>

    </div>
  </div>
</section>
